{"tid":2175402,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國務卿蓬佩奧點名批評匯控維持被制裁人士戶口","createTime":"2020-08-26T12:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T18:14:35.000Z","uid":26418,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d5dc8e15fce8ea980cd4204c51b0a711887a5f5f","tid":2175402,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:35:16.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧在Twitter發帖，指美國對於中國共產黨欺負他們的英國朋友及企業領袖而感到沮喪，他更批評，匯豐控股（0005）一方面維持那些因剥奪港人自由而被制裁的人的賬戶，另一方面卻關閉那些尋求自由的港人戶口。 <br />\n<br />\n較早前，美國財政部落實對包括特首林鄭月娥等11名中港官員加以制裁，彭博社則報道，在港運營的銀行正加強審查客戶，並引述消息稱，渣打及花旗正採取措施，暫停與一些受制裁官員有關的帳戶。"},{"pid":"d43755a8a08b822a04420177598b4c7ab5c5c940","tid":2175402,"uid":26418,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200826/s00010/aaa77e66b09f70a426295237ab7b2638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200826%2Fs00010%2Faaa77e66b09f70a426295237ab7b2638.jpg&h=39c7ab6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4218bad33ab6d5e008f8eec97b33cb10e30da97d","tid":2175402,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:37:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7a19c7d9b9330f53892484d7eeb9d4c0aab5343","tid":2175402,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"最後通牒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d8006db2c4e3ecdbf9afb3aba1227ce28da5a5","tid":2175402,"uid":289449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"罰錢啦，最好續日計"},{"pid":"39abeefbd67bb880890252886a6cef5d66ff0fcf","tid":2175402,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T12:48:21.000Z","msg":"講左出口<br />\n<br />\n自己看路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb80d040879e0e241102d2dd5b012584503eb8f","tid":2175402,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20